<L>__{exterior downtown los angeles early evening (still light)}
<A>__{the streets are crowded with business people on their way to homes and happy hours, buses and parking garages, showers and comforts. among the throngs, we find chris walking up grand street, backpack on his shoulders. we find he is not such an unusual sight, there are homeless to the left and homeless to the right.}
